HEADWORD: Impatible
<hw>Im*pat"i*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>impatibilis</ets>; pref. <ets>im-</ets> not + <ets>patibilis</ets>
